  "text": "Hannah Stryker / How-To Geek Amazon Echo Spot 2024 Brand Amazon Display 2.83” touch screen Dimensions 4.5\"W x 4.1\"D x 4.4\"H Weight 14.3oz The 2024 Amazon Echo Spot is a versatile smart display with a 5.5-inch touchscreen, ideal for video calls, streaming, and controlling smart home devices. With Alexa built-in, enjoy hands-free voice commands, rich sound quality, and seamless integration with your daily routines.  The Amazon Echo Spot smart speaker is currently at its best price of the year, dropping to $59.99 on Amazon. This is a 25% discount from its usual $79.99 price and beats any other price this year. It is a great deal for anyone looking for a useful smart alarm clock. The sale applies to the black and white models, but they are only discounted to $64.99. The blue version is the only one that hit its lowest price of the year at $59.99. If you've never owned an Echo Spot before, it's like an alarm that also acts as a hub. The Echo Spot has a customizable display that shows the time, weather, and song titles at a glance. You can change the clock face and pick from different colors to match your style. The price is really good for an alarm clock that does this much. Amazon says the device delivers \"big, vibrant sound,\" with rich audio, clear vocals, and deep bass, and while it does the job it needs to, I wouldn't expect it to be better than a speaker. Either way, the Echo Spot’s sound isn’t just for alarms; you can ask Alexa to play music, podcasts, and audiobooks, and you can control playback easily using the touchscreen. Alexa also works with smart home devices, letting users control compatible apps with voice commands or the touchscreen. For example, you can turn lights on or off, adjust the thermostat, and even set up automatic actions based on motion detection, all from the Echo Spot. You can check the weather, set reminders, and manage your daily routines using just your voice. The \"Ease into the Day\" feature gives a gentle wake-up with slowly brightening lights and music. You can also customize it to be even more in tune with what you like to wake up to. You can buy the Echo Spot clock on Amazon for $59.99. This is currently the newest model and is a big drop from its regular $79.99 price tag.",
